org.sql: SELECT current_ways.* FROM current_ways INNER JOIN current_way_nodes ON current_way_nodes.way_id = current_ways.id WHERE current_ways.visible = "$1" AND current_way_nodes.node_id = "$2" ORDER BY current_ways.id ASC
